1N.text:
How to ROTATE, SCALE, or MOVE objects
 - Open Update sprite
 - Drag Move, Rotate, or Scale under Update
 - Set name to the name of the object
 - Set rotation, scale, or move

1Q.text:
Render Visibility?
Set this to 0 to disable rendering for an object, set to 1 to enable.

1R.text:
Materials?
To set the color of a mesh, add a material with the name of the material found in the blender file. To find the name of the material, find it in the file with notepad.
